rows.label: tlk70000119_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey there!
I was just thinking about you!

rows.label: tlk70000119_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Actually, I'm going to Invidia soon.
I was going to pay you a visit!

rows.label: tlk70000119_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Sorry to change the subject, but do
you know where Rita-chan and Kaede-san
might have gone?

rows.label: tlk70000119_04_msg0004
rows.name:
They were in Gula until recently,
but haven't been seen for a while now...

rows.label: tlk70000119_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Eh? They're in Iira?
Helping Rita's dad?

rows.label: tlk70000119_04_msg0006
rows.name:
Oh, I see. So they're keeping busy.
I wonder if they'll head back here when
they're finished...
